<section>

<title>System requirements</title>

<para>&MiKTeXCurrentSeries; requires one of the following
&Windows; platforms:</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>&Windows7;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsVistaServicePack2; (all editions except Starter Edition)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsXPServicePack3; (all editions except Starter Edition)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2008R2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2008ServicePack2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2003R2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2003ServicePack2;</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

</section>

<section>

<title>Breaking changes</title>

<section>

<title>&Windows; Platforms</title>

<para>&Windows2000; is no longer supported.</para>

<para>&WindowsXP; platforms must have at least service pack&nbsp;3
installed.</para>

<para>&WindowsVista; platforms must have at least service pack&nbsp;2
installed.</para>

<para>&WindowsServer2003; platforms must have at least service
pack&nbsp;2 installed.</para>

<para>&WindowsServer2008; platforms must have at least service
pack&nbsp;2 installed.</para>

</section>

</section>

